<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">自上世纪80年代初团中央号召全国大学生在暑期开展“三下乡”社会实践活动起，到如今已经成为各大高校锻炼学生社会实践能力的一种常规性活动，也是学生综合素质的重要指标。江西软件职业技术大学作为全国第一所软件职业技术大学、全国首批15所本科层次职业教育高校之一，在暑假期间组织16支学生队伍以井冈山市的15个乡镇的文明实践为依托，深入到全省多个市县（区）的村镇，开展内容丰富、形式多样的社会实践活动。为群众办实事、做好事、解难事，服务区域经济社会发展，展现出朝气蓬勃的青春风采，为赣鄱乡村振兴注入青春力量。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2010%3A53%3A27640.png?Expires=2005354407&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ypEITxWgflnWyx2exf%2FvjGBQxOE%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学而促思</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">他们走进乡村调研振兴之路</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">7月3日上午，江西软件职业技术大学在创客中心路演大厅隆重举行暑期“三下乡”社会实践活动出征仪式。全校参加“三下乡”队伍的师生共300余人以此为起点，奔赴南昌、景德镇、九江、抚州、吉安、赣州各城区相关社区等基层一线，开启一场以“学思想、做调研、谋发展”为工作主线的助力乡村振兴之旅。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校16支三下乡队伍肩负着社会调研的重要任务。软件工程学院“实访探民情，实干助乡邻”暑期“三下乡”社会实践队走进井冈山市古城镇坳头村，从村中常住人口民生问题、基础设施问题、医疗保障问题及乡村振兴政策落实等多方面对坳头村当地村民进行乡村振兴调研。新媒体学院青春笃行实践队走进井冈山碧溪镇石坪存，对话村党委书记、寻访乡村振兴足迹、聆听乡贤故事，用人们喜闻乐见、通俗易懂的载体宣传党的创新理论；智能科技学院走进井冈山古田村，与村民畅谈乡村建设带来的变化，深入田间地头开展农耕实践，培养社会责任感和乡村情怀。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2011%3A02%3A03b7ce97b263ca57a7141bec15b2b611c.jpg?Expires=2005354924&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=lEMAbzHmNlncMcJ4qG9%2BDD8VAkQ%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">三下乡的师生们聚焦党的十八大以来党和国家取得的历史性成就、发生的历史性变革，以赣鄱大地为“课堂”，以脱贫攻坚重大历史性成就、全面建成小康社会决定性成就等为现实教材，开展社会观察、调查研究，深刻感悟党的领导、领袖领航、制度优势和人民力量的关键作用，更加坚定紧跟党奋进新征程的信心决心，奋力谱写中华民族伟大复兴的江西精彩篇章。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">以思促践</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">他们走近老幼播撒人间温情</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校三下乡队伍将课堂学习与乡村实践紧密结合，发扬实事求是精神，掌握密切联系群众方法，脚踏实地，自找苦吃，为加快推进农业农村现代化、全面建设社会主义现代化国家贡献青春力量。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2011%3A03%3A019ec8db12ebbed8299efad845522ce63.jpg?Expires=2005354983&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=tk3KLO%2BMg%2Fx9gGvlUV%2BurthZfSo%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校团委“青春伴文明”暑期社会实践队来到南昌市义坪村、江桥村、下罗村，为孩子们送去了温暖物资，并对孩子们进行安全知识和心理健康方面的宣传教育，与低保户及其家属亲切交谈送去关怀，并开展卫生整治活动；区块链学院“夏寻乌野”实践队在追寻红色足迹的同时，并为寻乌县上甲村童心港湾和香山村的孩子制作剪纸、教学手势舞，为老人们送去精彩的节目和甘甜的水果；学生会和社团管理中心“青春助航”社会实践队在九江市庐山市光明小学对小朋友进行舞蹈教学和游戏互动，并寻访老人为老人拍摄照片。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">以践促悟</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">他们追寻红色足迹凝聚奋进力量</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校持续深入学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，推进主题教育常态化长效化。暑期，学校三下乡队伍广泛学习宣传党的百年奋斗重大成就和历史经验，依托省内丰富的红色资源，开展重走红色足迹、追溯红色记忆、访谈红色人物、挖掘红色故事、体悟红色文化。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2011%3A07%3A5181c9b80dc25aedf839802dca3cbeddc.jpg?Expires=2005355271&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=HVNL1a07rQ7SWJ6AHutcR13prrw%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校记者团逐梦远航暑期社会实践队走进瑞昌市赛湖农场党员教育基地、新民社区知青馆和瑞昌剪纸博物馆感受红古绿三色辉映的赣鄱文化魅力；软件工程学院“筑梦童心”暑期“三下乡”社会实践队走进赣州市会昌县文武坝镇，探访红色旧址，聆听老一辈的红色故事，感受浓厚的红色文化底蕴。智能科技学院“情系赣畲，萤火温井”社会实践队的队员们开展了“重走长征路”主题活动。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">知行合一</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">他们身体力行“浇灌”科教之花</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校三下乡的队伍们在开展社会观察、调查研究之外，还前往村民经常聚集的地方，精心设计，开展有内涵、有人气的宣传教育活动。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2011%3A15%3A218189f7146836508464112190cc78b5d.jpg?Expires=2005355721&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=FGZ%2FjV7X%2BXtU2IfUS%2BhdoEUzKDI%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">网络工程学院“青春燃梦，‘乡’约盛夏”实践队来到丰城市丽村镇龙兴村宣讲党的二十大精神、意燃气使用安全、夏季防溺水和防范诈骗等内容；学校“传统文化会说话”宣讲实践队参观了海昏侯遗址博物馆、八大山人纪念馆、陈云旧居陈列馆、梅汝璈故居，来到青云谱区岱山街道君湖社区开展防溺水宣传活动；经济管理学院“青衿筑梦”志愿服务队前往井冈山茅坪镇，开展“祖国旗帜在我心，思想引领见行动”、“弘扬传统文化，体验科技创新”、“练中国书法，承传统文化”、推广宣传普通话系列主题活动。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">通过一系列宣讲活动，引领群众更加深刻领悟“两个确立”的决定性意义，更加信心满怀地紧跟党的核心、人民领袖奋进新征程、建功新时代。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">敢闯敢为</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">他们弘扬赣鄱青年担当与力量</span></strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">去年9月，江西软件职业技术大学井冈山数字经济产业学院在红旗漫卷的井冈山下举行，标志着先锋软件集团、江西软件职业技术大学正式开始探索革命老区发展数字经济产业新区的新模式。因而，今年学校三下乡活动遍及井冈山市15个乡镇。同学们奋斗激扬的青春风采照亮了革命老区井冈山，而永垂不朽的井冈山精神淬炼出更加坚定的理想和信念。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-07-22%2011%3A22%3A1556c897269746001aed5e63d89e54de5.jpg?Expires=2005356135&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=dD7zBRdg4810aRjbfu3OY6Fv2R8%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">VR与艺术学院“筑梦远征·艺同前行”实践队在上饶市横峰县岑阳镇朝堂村，用自己所学知识为当地特色农产品——马家柚设计宣传海报，开展应急救助教育、文明礼仪教育和爱国主义教育；区块链学院“夏寻乌野”实践队到寻乌县王别村清理着河流中、河道旁的每一处垃圾，充分发挥不怕苦、不怕累、不怕脏的精神，以实际行动践行&quot;河小清“志愿服务精神。同学们在在实践大课堂中受教育、长才干、做贡献，为乡村振兴注入新鲜活力。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">活动开展以来，气氛十分热烈，江西软件职业技术大学三下乡队伍的优秀品质不仅获得了当地村民的赞赏，更吸引了地方媒体乃至省级、国家级媒体的报导宣传。据统计，各实践团队的事迹被广电总台国际在线、央广网、学习强国平台、江西教育电视台、江西新闻、江南都市报、井冈山融媒、社会实践网和各地官方媒体等报道40余次。报道角度涉及乡村发展变化、关爱乡村留守儿童、非遗传承、乡村振兴、爱心支教、红色研学等多个方面。另外16支实践团队制作调研视频20余个，形成调研报告16份。这种多角度、多层面、多方式的报道，全方位展示出江软青年以身报国的实际行动，也成为弘扬赣鄱青年的时代担当与青春力量的新窗口。</span></p><p><br/></p>